### Sample Payment Requests for Testing

### 1. Valid Payment Request - USD
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-001",
  "amount": 100.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Test payment for order #12345"
}

### 2. Valid Payment Request - EUR
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-002",
  "amount": 250.75,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "description": "Hotel booking payment"
}

### 3. Valid Payment Request - Large Amount
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-003",
  "amount": 9999.99,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "High-value transaction test"
}

### 4. Valid Payment Request - Small Amount
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-004",
  "amount": 0.01,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Minimum amount test"
}

### 5. Valid Payment Request - Different Currency (GBP)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-005",
  "amount": 75.25,
  "currency": "GBP",
  "description": "British Pound payment test"
}

### 6. Valid Payment Request - Minimal Fields
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-006",
  "amount": 50.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Basic payment test"
}

### 7. Edge Case - Zero Amount (might be invalid)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-007",
  "amount": 0.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Zero amount test"
}

### 8. Edge Case - Negative Amount (should be invalid)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-008",
  "amount": -50.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Negative amount test"
}

### 9. Edge Case - Missing ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Payment without ID"
}

### 10. Edge Case - Missing Amount
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-010",
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Payment without amount"
}

### 11. Edge Case - Missing Currency
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-011",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "description": "Payment without currency"
}

### 12. Edge Case - Empty Description
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-012",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": ""
}

### 13. Edge Case - Null Values
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": null,
  "amount": null,
  "currency": null,
  "description": null
}

### 14. Edge Case - Invalid Currency Code
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-014",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "INVALID",
  "description": "Invalid currency test"
}

### 15. Edge Case - Very Long Description
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-015",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "This is a very long description that might test the limits of the system and see how it handles extremely long text inputs that could potentially cause issues with database storage or processing limitations in the payment system"
}

### 16. Edge Case - Special Characters in Description
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-016",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Payment with special chars: !@#$%^&*()_+-=[]{}|;':\",./<>?"
}

### 17. Edge Case - Unicode Characters
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-017",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Payment with unicode: 测试支付 🚀 €£¥"
}

### 18. Edge Case - Empty JSON Object
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 19. Edge Case - Invalid JSON Format
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-019",
  "amount": "invalid-number",
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Invalid amount format"
}

### 20. Valid Payment Request - Multiple Decimal Places
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "payment-020",
  "amount": 123.456789,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Multiple decimal places test"
}